description: Market Bar-B-Que’s brick & mortar location has been a magnificent Minneapolis landmark for over 70 years, and now they’re makin’ their best eats out on the streets. That same brick pit-smoked meat that you love and know, can now even be enjoyed on the go!You’ll find Pork Ribs, Sandwiches with Pulled Pork or Brisket, and finger-lickin’ BBQ Chicken Wings, along with an assortment of delightful sides, like Baked Beans, Mac & Cheese, Candied Yams, and more. So be sure to make your next event extra tasty, and invite the Market Bar-B-Que Truck to bring their delicious grub straight to you.
name: Market Bar-B-Que Food Truck
